    from Bäbler, Balbina (Göttingen). "Nicostratus." Brill's New Pauly. Antiquity volumes edited by: Hubert Cancik and Helmuth Schneider . Brill, 2008. Brill Online. Tufts University Library. 07 May 2008</mads:note>
